snippet.title: Brendan Fraser Has The Best Reaction Over His Online Support
snippet.description:
The internet cannot get enough of Brendan Fraser's return to the big screen in Martin Scorsese's upcoming western "Killers of the Flower Moon". During an interview with Lindley Key, the actor had the sweetest reaction to being told about the internet's support after previously revealing he was a little anxious to play the part.

#BrendanFraser #KillersOfTheFlowerMoon
